rice","fundHeader.inav.time":"Time","fundHeader.inav.title":"Intraday NAV &amp; Market Price","fundHeader.key-benefits":"Why {0}?","fundHeader.key-benefits.ishares-fund-data":"Why {0}?","fundHeader.keyDocuments.EUPRIIP":"","fundHeader.keyDocuments.FundUpdate~Prospectus":"Subscribe to fund announcements","fundHeader.mstarRatingOverall.asOf":"","fundHeader.mstarRatingOverall.available ":"","fundHeader.mstarRatingOverall.infobubble":"{0} received a Morningstar Rating of {5} stars for the 3-year period, {7} for the 5-year period and {9} for the 10-year period, rated against {6}, {8} and {10} {4} Funds, respectively. Performance results represent past performance and are no guarantee of future results.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;For each U.S.-domiciled fund with at least a 3-year history, Morningstar calculates a Morningstar RatingTM based on a Morningstar Risk-Adjusted Return measure that accounts for variation in a fund&#39;s monthly performance (including the effects of sales charges, loads and redemption fees), placing more emphasis on downward variations and rewarding consistent performance. The top 10% of funds in each category receive five stars, the next 22.5% receive four stars, the next 35% receive three stars, the next 22.5% receive two stars and the bottom 10% receive one star. (Each share class is counted as a fraction of one fund within this scale and rated separately, which may cause slight variations in the distribution percentages.) The Overall Morningstar Rating for a fund is derived from a weighted-average of the performance figures associated with its 3-, 5- and 10-year (if applicable) Morningstar Rating metrics.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Morningstar Ratings are for the share classes cited only; other classes may have different ratings.","fundHeader.mstarRatingOverall.notAvailable ":"","fundHeader.mstarRatingOverall.title":"Morningstar Rating","fundHeader.noDisclaimerMsg":"Risk disclosures and fund objective on this page might be missing due to a system error.   Please refer to the respective Prospectus / Offering Documents for such information while we recover our platform.  We apologise for any inconvenience caused.","fundHeader.priips-product-type.objective":"","fundHeader.priips-product-type.objective.text.blk-mutual-fund-data":"","fundHeader.readyToBuy":"Ready To Buy?","fundHeader.readyToBuy.tooltip":"You can trade this ETF now.","fundHeader.shareClass":"","fundHeader.shareClassSelector":"Share Class:","fundHeader.tenReasons":"Reason to\nPurchase this fund","fundHeader.title":"","fundHeader.yearToDate.infobubble":"YTD (year to date) is a period, starting from the beginning of the current calendar year, and continuing up to the prior day&#39;s close.","fundHeader.ytd":"YTD: ","fundamentalsAndRisk.header.title":"Characteristics","holdings.header.title":"Holdings","howToBuy.button":"Learn More","howToBuy.button.ticker":"","howToBuy.modalContent.col-right.buy-button-content":"Buy now on Fidelity","howToBuy.modalContent.col-right.col-details1":"iShares funds are available through online brokerage firms.","howToBuy.modalContent.col-right.col-details2":"All iShares ETFs and ETPs trade commission free online through Fidelity.","howToBuy.modalContent.col-right.col-details3":"By clicking on the button below, you will leave BlackRock’s website.","howToBuy.modalContent.col-right.col-heading":"Buy through your brokerage","investNow.buyEtfButton":"","investNow.buyEtfText":"","investNow.howWouldYouLikeToInvest":"","investNow.investNowButton":"","investNow.savingsPlanButton":"","investNow.savingsPlanText":"","keyDocuments.all-documents":"All Documents","keyDocuments.cmdtSecReports":"Periodic SEC Reports","keyDocuments.faicDocumentsLink":"All Documents","keyDocuments.faicDocumentsLink.link":"https://www2.blackrock.com/us/faic/ECON?appname=estudio&amp;blkifrmurl=https://estudio.blackrock.com/bin/search.asp?Venue=FP_ML","keyDocuments.gsgSecReports":"Periodic SEC Reports","keyDocuments.iauBarList":"Gold Bar List","keyDocuments.iauSec